<div class="checklist">
    <label><input type="checkbox"> 1. Convince Mum with a calm, well-thought-out plan.</label>
    <label><input type="checkbox"> 2. List what Mum will be responsible for (vet, transport, emergencies).</label>
    <label><input type="checkbox"> 3. List what Sister will be responsible for (and get her agreement).</label>
    <label><input type="checkbox"> 4. Write what YOU will do daily (feeding, water, walking, poo cleanup, training).</label>
    <label><input type="checkbox"> 5. Draw a map showing where the fence will go.</label>
    <label><input type="checkbox"> 6. Keep house tidy ‚Äì kitchen bench clear before school and before bed.</label>
    <label><input type="checkbox"> 7. Research dog care (feeding, vaccines, desexing, worming, training, costs).</label>
    <label><input type="checkbox"> 8. Save your own money to contribute to costs.</label>
    <label><input type="checkbox"> 9. Create a weekly routine chart for feeding, walks, and cleaning.</label>
    <label><input type="checkbox"> 10. Prove responsibility for 3 months without reminders.</label>
